fading, only the eyes remaining.<br>
<br>
</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;Yes, Mistress&quot; <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>said Binuven, the hatred in his voice clear as day.<br>
<br>
</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->&quot;Begin the preparations at once!&quot; <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>she commanded.<br>
<br>
